+// We have interfaces for the following instructions:
+// - NativeInstruction
+// - - NativeCall
+// - - NativeMovConstReg
+// - - NativeMovRegMem
+// - - NativeJump
+// - - NativeGeneralJump
+// - - NativeIllegalInstruction
+// - - NativeCallTrampolineStub
+// - - NativeMembar
+// - - NativeFenceI
